# User Stories

### User Story 1

As a Sales Manager, I want to view total sales revenue by region so that I can identify high-performing and underperforming markets.

### User Story 2

As a Regional Manager, I want to monitor monthly sales trends so that I can forecast future performance and plan resources effectively.

### User Story 3

As an Executive, I want to view key performance indicators on a single dashboard so that I can quickly assess business performance.

### User Story 4

As a Product Manager, I want to identify top-performing products so that I can prioritize inventory and marketing investments.

### User Story 5

As a Customer Success Manager, I want to analyze customer purchasing behavior so that I can improve customer retention strategies.
